1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:40,530
[Bazaar Beloved Birds]

3
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:43,289
[Episode 23]

4
00:01:46,789 --> 00:01:47,880
Master, I ask for your punishment.

5
00:01:49,539 --> 00:01:51,060
The rest of you may leave.

6
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,580
Ye Mo, you stay.

7
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:04,570
Get up.

8
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:08,110
Master.

9
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:11,070
Ye Mo.

10
00:02:11,610 --> 00:02:13,530
You've been following me since you were little.

11
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,710
How do you feel about the way I treat you?

12
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:17,710
I feel deeply grateful and indebted for your kindness.

13
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:21,630
A few days ago,

14
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,600
I said I would take you as my adopted son.

15
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,079
Do you still remember it?

16
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:26,220
Yes.

17
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,660
Since

18
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,480
we have become father and son,

19
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:32,380
I will now tell you

20
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:34,260
the secret of the Red Jade of Cangqiong.

21
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,400
The secret?

22
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,870
Thirteen years ago,

23
00:02:40,070 --> 00:02:41,790
the Golden Blade Sect was ruthlessly wiped out,

24
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:46,250
and it was done by me and the Mirror Department.

25
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:47,320
What?

26
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:49,350
Surprised?

27
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:51,180
Back then, Liu Chengfan approached me,

28
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,160
asking me to handle the Golden Blade Sect,

29
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:55,110
and he would assist me in unifying the martial arts world.

30
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,620
It happened to provide me

31
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:58,390
with an opportunity to advance my plan.

32
00:02:58,820 --> 00:02:59,430
But...

33
00:03:00,230 --> 00:03:01,230
wasn't it the Demon Boy's doing?

34
00:03:02,110 --> 00:03:03,270
That was just a surface appearance.

35
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:05,020
Do you know

36
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,830
why I did that back then?

37
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:08,320
To be the Chief of Sects.

38
00:03:11,270 --> 00:03:12,110
Back then,

39
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:15,020
after we, the trio of Master Knife, Sword and Laugh unified the martial arts world,

40
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,520
Feng Lie hid a bunch of treasures

41
00:03:17,790 --> 00:03:18,910
in a certain place.

42
00:03:19,070 --> 00:03:21,120
Inside, there were significant loads of gold and silver,

43
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,579
as well as extraordinary weapons.

44
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,760
More importantly,

45
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:27,070
a martial arts manual kept secret by the trio
was also stored there.

46
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,130
Legend has it

47
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:30,170
that whoever gets these treasures

48
00:03:30,290 --> 00:03:31,450
will become

49
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:33,010
the true supreme in the martial arts world.

50
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:35,540
The way to find these treasures

51
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:39,010
lies within the three pieces of the Red Jade of Cangqiong.

52
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:41,710
However, there was a setback
during the siege of the Golden Blade Sect

53
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,710
thirteen years ago.

54
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,620
My duel with Feng Lie led

55
00:03:49,690 --> 00:03:51,140
to the loss of all my martial skills.

56
00:03:52,829 --> 00:03:53,790
Unfortunately,

57
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,570
although we wiped out the Golden Blade Sect,

58
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,079
the two pieces of the Red Jade
belonging to the Knife Master and the Laugh Master

59
00:03:59,329 --> 00:04:00,370
went missing.

60
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:02,230
So, for all these years,

61
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:03,710
I've been searching for the whereabouts

62
00:04:03,730 --> 00:04:05,510
of these two pieces of the Red Jade of Cangqiong.

63
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,550
Now,

64
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,970
I have finally found the Red Jade of the Knife Master,

65
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:11,500
and the only one missing is that of the Laugh Master.

66
00:04:12,530 --> 00:04:13,260
Ye Mo,

67
00:04:13,950 --> 00:04:16,230
help me find the last piece of the Red Jade,

68
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,950
then the whole world

69
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,810
will be ours.

70
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,390
Master, you can rest assured.

71
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,600
I will surely help you

72
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:24,650
accomplish your grand goals in the martial arts world.

73
00:04:27,990 --> 00:04:29,590
Thank you for saving me.

74
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:30,890
I will never forget your assistance.

75
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,100
No need for formality.

76
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:34,290
I promised Miss Yu to save you,

77
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:35,280
so I must keep my word.

78
00:04:35,909 --> 00:04:37,460
Even if the Heavenly King comes himself,

79
00:04:37,530 --> 00:04:38,320
I will still save you.

80
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,220
This is called professional ethics.

81
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,390
Mr. Chen,

82
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:45,360
your money...

83
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:46,670
What's wrong with it?

84
00:04:46,909 --> 00:04:47,800
Nothing.

85
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:50,710
I've been keeping it for you all this time,

86
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:51,820
but,

87
00:04:51,909 --> 00:04:54,500
your money was taken back to the Lu Ming Manor by Ye Yunqing.

88
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:58,740
But don't worry.

89
00:04:58,870 --> 00:04:59,590
I will make sure to give you

90
00:04:59,590 --> 00:05:00,670
what is rightfully yours.

91
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:03,260
Fine.

92
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,480
Let Ye Yunqing

93
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,830
keep it for me for a while.

94
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:08,110
The money is mine,

95
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,190
and no one can take it away from me.

96
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,870
Eventually, our Whirlwind Stronghold

97
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:13,390
will bring down his Lu Ming Manor.

98
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:15,190
Sure thing.

99
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:15,960
Sure thing.

100
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,600
Mr. Chen,

101
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,430
why do you sound like a bandit?

102
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,170
What do you mean?

103
00:05:22,770 --> 00:05:25,030
Chen has officially become a bandit now.

104
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,730
Didn't we initially agree to

105
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:29,860
await your return and welcome you?

106
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,210
But instead of your arrival,

107
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:33,450
we came across Mr. Chen, who was covered in blood.

108
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,560
So, we brought him back to the Whirlwind Stronghold.

109
00:05:35,670 --> 00:05:36,480
A few days ago,

110
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,230
we saw Ye Yunqing leading a group

111
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:40,240
towards Xianyun City.

112
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:41,630
We felt something was wrong,

113
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,060
so we followed him.

114
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:47,310
Th-that's... right!

115
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:53,920
Mr. Chen... is now...

116
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,620
That's right.

117
00:05:54,710 --> 00:05:56,470
He's our boss now,

118
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,630
and I have taken a backseat.

119
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,770
Boss?

120
00:06:02,350 --> 00:06:02,790
Yes.

121
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,370
Wang Zheng, Wang Qiang, and I

122
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:06,760
have sworn friendship.

123
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:08,910
I've also fallen in love with the days

124
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:10,210
of devouring meat and indulging in heavy drinking.

125
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:11,860
It's so satisfying.

126
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:16,870
Yun,

127
00:06:17,570 --> 00:06:18,920
if you want to join us,

128
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:20,500
the two of us

129
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:22,540
can sit together in this position.

130
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,580
You're not included.

131
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,250
All right, all right.

132
00:06:29,710 --> 00:06:30,870
Let's think about

133
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:31,930
what we should do next.

134
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,060
People from Lu Ming Manor and the Mirror Department

135
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:35,220
are on their way here now.

136
00:06:35,590 --> 00:06:36,390
That's right.

137
00:06:37,409 --> 00:06:37,950
Xixi,

138
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:40,520
there might be something very important inside,

139
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,330
related to us

140
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,870
and the entire martial arts world.

141
00:06:45,659 --> 00:06:46,510
Can you open it?

142
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:49,409
Isn't this my mechanical ball?

143
00:06:49,850 --> 00:06:51,320
It was left by your father, Mr. Hai.

144
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,460
But I've been studying it since I was a kid,

145
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:56,650
and I couldn't open it.

146
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:57,470
Seriously?

147
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,540
Is it so difficult to crack?

148
00:06:59,470 --> 00:07:00,510
This mechanical ball

149
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,900
is assembled with mortise and tenon joints.

150
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,430
Touch one part, and the whole thing moves.

151
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,990
We need to find the crucial piece,

152
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:05,940
otherwise, it won't open.

153
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,330
How about just cutting it open?

154
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,960
No.

155
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,540
The mechanical ball has mechanisms inside.

156
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,850
If it experiences external impact,

157
00:07:10,930 --> 00:07:12,400
the thing within will be automatically destroyed.

158
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,370
Then, what should we do?

159
00:07:15,890 --> 00:07:16,820
Let me think about it.

160
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,990
You've been thinking about it for over a decade,
and you still haven't figured out a solution.

161
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:22,510
That's because back then,
Yu Zhao wouldn't let me play with it.

162
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,350
But now I can play with it, right?

163
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:24,550
Tell me if you need anything.

164
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,300
Great.

165
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:26,470
I need all the books

166
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:28,630
related to mechanical arts available in the market.

167
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,350
That's easy.

168
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:30,450
Miss Yu,

169
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:32,800
I'll send the whole gang

170
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,000
to buy those books for you tomorrow.

171
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:35,650
I guarantee that not a single one will be missed.

172
00:07:37,409 --> 00:07:38,650
Thanks, I'll leave it to you.

173
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:40,170
I'll repay you double when the time comes.

174
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:41,409
It's not a big deal.

175
00:07:45,350 --> 00:07:45,840
This way.

176
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:47,310
Everyone, this way, please.

177
00:07:47,330 --> 00:07:48,250
Let's go for a drink.

178
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,070
Let's go.

179
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:53,940
[Lu Ming Manor]

180
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,159
What exactly

181
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,560
are you up to?

182
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:59,550
You've been following me since this morning.

183
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:00,720
What's your plan?

184
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,540
This is part of my plan.

185
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,790
What plan?

186
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,380
You literally look like you're on a spring outing.

187
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:08,550
They're here.

188
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:09,930
Let's sit down first.

189
00:08:17,180 --> 00:08:18,160
Get closer to me.

190
00:08:19,530 --> 00:08:21,090
This is part of the plan.

191
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:22,920
I'll shout out numbers,

192
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,360
and we'll shake our heads to the pace of "one, two."

193
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:25,190
Ready.

194
00:08:25,610 --> 00:08:27,480
One, two.

195
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:29,770
One, two.

196
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:31,380
One, two.

197
00:08:32,770 --> 00:08:33,590
You're still a kid.

198
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:34,960
This is not suitable for you.

199
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:36,830
Uncle, don't block my sight.

200
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:38,750
This is already the 26th time

201
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:40,850
they've kissed today.

202
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,159
Indeed.

203
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:45,000
What's wrong with Young Master?

204
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,860
He was so unwilling yesterday,

205
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:47,760
but look at him now,

206
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,350
he's fallen into the land of romance

207
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:52,000
and unwilling to get out.

208
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,350
He's a man, after all.

209
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:57,280
Miss Liu is also a stunning beauty.

210
00:08:57,890 --> 00:08:59,330
How can Young Master, full of vigor,

211
00:08:59,690 --> 00:09:01,180
possibly resist such a temptation?

212
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:03,940
Shut up. You sound like you know everything.

213
00:09:05,010 --> 00:09:06,110
Keep a close eye on them.

214
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,500
If anything goes wrong,

215
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,620
Master will definitely give you a hard time.

216
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,240
I know. I know.

217
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,670
One, two.

218
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,940
Why are you blushing?

219
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:19,470
I... I'm not blushing.

220
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:21,870
Let me tell you.

221
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,000
If I find out that you don't have a plan in the end,

222
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,270
you'll see how I deal with you.

223
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,670
Don't worry.

224
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:28,550
Would I ever take advantage of you?

225
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,190
They are still watching us.

226
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:32,110
Ready, let's continue.

227
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:35,990
One, two, one, two.

228
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,290
Great!

229
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,240
Young Master Feng and Daughter,

230
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:02,430
seeing this letter is like seeing me in person.

231
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:03,830
Since

232
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:05,630
you've opened this letter today,

233
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:08,440
there are some things I want you to know.

234
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,720
No more buts.

235
00:11:10,430 --> 00:11:11,720
Let me tell you the truth.

236
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:15,150
The Mirror Department has long wanted to take down the Golden Blade Sect.

237
00:11:15,350 --> 00:11:16,660
No one can stop it.

238
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,080
What do you want me to do?

239
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:24,390
I heard that Mr. Hai

240
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,160
is a savvy businessman,

241
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:27,770
and he is also highly skilled in pharmacy.

242
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:30,860
He's good at medicine and poison.

243
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:31,990
Especially

244
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:33,910
skilled in poisoning.

245
00:11:35,430 --> 00:11:36,430
So?

246
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,580
So,

247
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:39,800
I want you to prepare a poisonous insect

248
00:11:40,450 --> 00:11:41,950
for Feng Lie's eldest son,

249
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:43,590
Feng Zihe.

250
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,190
What?

251
00:11:46,970 --> 00:11:49,320
I heard that Feng Lie's eldest son

252
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:50,820
is incredibly skilled in martial arts.

253
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,480
If we can drive him insane through poisoning,

254
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:56,630
we can shape him into the Demon Boy in the martial arts world,

255
00:11:56,830 --> 00:11:58,230
causing all sects

256
00:11:58,470 --> 00:12:00,240
to turn against the Golden Blade Sect.

257
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:02,320
But if we do that,

258
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:03,970
the Golden Blade Sect will be wiped out.

259
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,940
I can't do such a shameful thing!

260
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:14,680
Mr. Hai,

261
00:12:15,450 --> 00:12:17,130
if you don't think for yourself,

262
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:20,290
you should think for others.

263
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:23,440
I heard that Mr. Hai's daughter is five years old now.

264
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:24,550
You...

265
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:29,870
You can't harm my wife and kid.

266
00:12:30,530 --> 00:12:31,790
This is the rule of the martial arts world.

267
00:12:31,810 --> 00:12:32,810
Rule?

268
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:35,210
Rules are set by people.

269
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:41,130
I believe Mr. Hai

270
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,820
will definitely make the right choice.

271
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:50,640
In the end, I made this poison that he asked for.

272
00:12:50,950 --> 00:12:53,150
And Young Master Feng gradually fell into darkness,

273
00:12:53,570 --> 00:12:54,940
and became an enemy of the martial arts world.

274
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:57,670
The conflicts among the major sects and the Golden Blade Sect

275
00:12:57,670 --> 00:12:58,790
became increasingly intense,

276
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:01,960
finally erupting

277
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:03,030
on that night 14 years ago.

278
00:13:03,230 --> 00:13:05,550
All sects confronted the Golden Blade Sect,

279
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:08,420
and at this moment, people from the Mirror Department

280
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:10,560
and Lu Ming Manor took advantage to instigate,

281
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,850
leading to a horrible tragedy.

282
00:13:13,070 --> 00:13:13,700
Yu Zhao.

283
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:16,180
What's wrong?

284
00:13:17,070 --> 00:13:18,460
Thirteen years ago,

285
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,000
my father...

286
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,580
This has nothing to do with you.

287
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,240
Besides, Mr. Hai also saved me,

288
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,260
which can be seen as some form of amends.

289
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:29,270
Even if Mr. Hai didn't save me,

290
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:31,740
it wouldn't affect us at all.

291
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,740
Brother, what's your plan next?

292
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,970
I want to issue a Jianghu Summon Order

293
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:47,750
and organize a Martial Arts Competition.

294
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,720
What?

295
00:13:49,310 --> 00:13:50,510
A Martial Arts Competition?

296
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:52,040
But

297
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,070
on what grounds can we issue a summon order?

298
00:13:55,980 --> 00:13:57,170
Because I'm the Demon Boy.

299
00:13:58,850 --> 00:14:00,500
I'll summon them in the name of the Demon Boy,

300
00:14:00,830 --> 00:14:02,100
and the location will be the Golden Blade Sect.

301
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:04,510
Since that's where it all began,

302
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,990
let's put an end to it there.

303
00:14:08,310 --> 00:14:08,950
Besides,

304
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:12,330
I donâ€™t want to implicate all of you from the Whirlwind Stronghold.

305
00:14:12,470 --> 00:14:13,220
Manager,

306
00:14:13,830 --> 00:14:14,630
you're being too formal with us.

307
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,150
We're like family now.

308
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:19,030
But there will be a lot of people there that day,

309
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:21,390
including members
from the Mirror Department and Lu Ming Manor.

310
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,020
It's okay.

311
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,350
The more people come, the better.

312
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:26,100
Because I want to publicly reveal

313
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:28,600
the content of this letter at the Martial Arts Competition.

314
00:14:28,930 --> 00:14:30,730
Back then, all sects targeted the Golden Blade Sect

315
00:14:31,190 --> 00:14:32,270
due to the schemes of the Mirror Department

316
00:14:32,270 --> 00:14:33,790
and Lu Ming Manor.

317
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:37,150
I'll reveal the truth at the assembly,

318
00:14:37,230 --> 00:14:39,200
and give a closure for all those people

319
00:14:39,230 --> 00:14:40,150
who died because of that incident.

320
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:43,230
What is this?

321
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:46,350
This is the Jianghu Summon Order.

322
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:50,910
I know.

323
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:53,580
Everyone in the martial arts world has received it.

324
00:14:54,470 --> 00:14:56,440
What do you think Feng Zihe wants to do?

325
00:14:57,860 --> 00:14:58,460
Well...

326
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:02,340
I really don't know.

327
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:03,250
You don't know?

328
00:15:04,410 --> 00:15:05,510
Then, let me tell you.

329
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:08,360
He must have evidence related to us

330
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:10,190
from 13 years ago.

331
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,230
If he presents this evidence

332
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:15,460
to the major sects,

333
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:19,520
we will become enemies of the martial arts world.

334
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:22,190
My Lord, you can rest assured.

335
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:23,940
No matter what Feng Zihe wants to do,

336
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:26,790
everything is under control.

337
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,940
I think you can't even protect yourself now.

338
00:15:33,430 --> 00:15:34,930
I'll give you one last chance.

339
00:15:35,470 --> 00:15:37,470
I hope you can cleanly and thoroughly get this job done

340
00:15:38,130 --> 00:15:40,050
at the upcoming Martial Arts Competition.

341
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:40,900
My Lord,

342
00:15:41,620 --> 00:15:43,300
I have a plan,

343
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,660
but it requires your assistance.

344
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:46,750
Tell me.

345
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:54,120
[The Golden Blade Sect]

346
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,820
According to the rules of the Martial Arts Competition,

347
00:15:59,310 --> 00:16:01,470
each sect leader can only bring two followers into the venue,

348
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,760
and the rest will wait outside.

349
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:05,850
We're all prominent figures in the martial arts world,

350
00:16:07,230 --> 00:16:08,710
I don't think any of us will disregard the rules, right?

351
00:16:10,130 --> 00:16:11,260
I'm not afraid of him.

352
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:12,350
Let's get in.

353
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,569
Behave yourselves, both of you.

354
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,560
Don't make trouble.

355
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:25,800
Don't worry.

356
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:56,750
Demon Boy.

357
00:17:57,990 --> 00:17:59,470
How dare you organize the Martial Arts Competition?

358
00:17:59,910 --> 00:18:00,920
What do you want?

359
00:18:05,320 --> 00:18:05,860
Everyone,

360
00:18:06,940 --> 00:18:07,970
I'm Feng Zihe,

361
00:18:08,630 --> 00:18:09,910
the eldest son of the leader of the Golden Blade Sect,

362
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:11,870
Feng Lie, also known as the Knife Master.

363
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,960
This is my younger brother, Feng Zihuan.

364
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:19,110
Demon Boy, what do you want?

365
00:18:19,390 --> 00:18:20,270
No matter what,

366
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:21,640
I won't let you off the hook today.

367
00:18:21,990 --> 00:18:23,510
I must act in the name of justice!

368
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:25,080
What are you talking about?

369
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,310
You keep calling him the Demon Boy.

370
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,240
Do you have any manners?

371
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,590
Didn't your parents raise you properly?

372
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:29,450
Behave yourself.

373
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,240
Over the years,

374
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:34,100
it seems that there has been a misunderstanding about me.

375
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:36,040
Today, I've gathered you all here

376
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:38,100
to resolve this misunderstanding.

377
00:18:41,190 --> 00:18:42,190
Young Master Feng,

378
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:43,930
how do you want to resolve it?

379
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:46,030
Back then, when you fell into darkness,

380
00:18:46,030 --> 00:18:47,310
you killed so many people of different sects.

381
00:18:48,190 --> 00:18:49,720
I'm afraid it's not a misunderstanding.

382
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,390
You're right, Master Yun.

383
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:53,820
But the fact that I fell into darkness

384
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,360
was not as simple as it seemed.

385
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:59,930
This is a handwritten letter by the former leader of Yixiao Hall,

386
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,670
Hai Liyuan, also known as the Laugh Master.

387
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:03,710
It reveals the truth

388
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,460
about me falling into darkness.

389
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:06,870
Young Master Feng,

390
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:08,700
how can you prove that

391
00:19:08,990 --> 00:19:10,510
this letter was written by the Laugh Master?

392
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:21,290
This is the Laugh Master's Red Jade of Cangqiong.

393
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,080
If you say so.

394
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,960
But I don't think that's real.

395
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:30,470
You'll know once you read this letter.

396
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:33,330
There are some special symbols in it.

397
00:19:34,390 --> 00:19:35,510
Special symbols?

398
00:19:44,530 --> 00:19:45,300
Masters,

399
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:46,830
please, this way.

400
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:49,250
Okay.

401
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:50,460
This way.

402
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:56,710
Are you ready?

403
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:57,390
Yes.

404
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:58,710
The Mirror Commander has arrived.

405
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,680
I almost fell asleep.

406
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:18,300
Wake up, wake up.

407
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:20,280
What are you doing?

408
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:22,770
If both of us fall asleep,

409
00:20:23,170 --> 00:20:24,350
who will keep an eye on them?

410
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,500
Look at them.

411
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:28,370
Is it necessary to keep an eye on them?

412
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:31,210
They are always lovey-dovey,

413
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,230
and doing nothing.

414
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:35,460
Just go to sleep.

415
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,740
What are you waiting for?

416
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:48,750
You've been here just staring at the trees.

417
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:57,470
The wind is here.

418
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:02,010
Come with me.

419
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:13,790
What's that sound?

420
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:17,480
Maybe it was just a dream.

421
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,160
Un-uncle!

422
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,530
Th-they are gone!

423
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,230
Where are they?

424
00:21:25,230 --> 00:21:26,430
I... I don't know!

425
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:28,060
Calm down.

426
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:29,760
It's alright.

427
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:32,150
Our Lu Ming Manor is heavily guarded.

428
00:21:32,910 --> 00:21:34,190
I don't think the Young Master and Miss Liu

429
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:35,470
will be able to escape.

430
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:37,260
Unless...

431
00:21:38,890 --> 00:21:40,140
they can fly out, right?

432
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:43,670
That's right.

433
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,930
This letter does contain the special symbols of our sect.

434
00:21:46,760 --> 00:21:47,810
I found ours too.

435
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:48,940
So, does that mean

436
00:21:49,460 --> 00:21:50,540
it was really...

437
00:21:54,150 --> 00:21:55,310
You've read the letter.

438
00:21:56,120 --> 00:21:56,720
What do you think?

439
00:21:56,810 --> 00:21:57,690
So it was you who was behind this.

440
00:21:57,990 --> 00:21:59,360
You've tricked us into misunderstanding

441
00:21:59,690 --> 00:22:00,840
Young Master Feng for so many years!

442
00:22:01,940 --> 00:22:02,460
Master,

443
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:05,330
I don't understand what you said.

444
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:07,390
Stop pretending.

445
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,710
The incident where Young Master Feng fell into darkness

446
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:11,870
was orchestrated by you and the Mirror Department!

447
00:22:14,610 --> 00:22:16,850
You believe it was me just because of this forged letter?

448
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,980
Forged letter?

449
00:22:23,950 --> 00:22:24,840
Take a look yourself.

450
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:28,450
These are all

451
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,700
special symbols from all different sects.

452
00:22:31,710 --> 00:22:32,750
You're the Sword Master,

453
00:22:33,140 --> 00:22:34,220
you shouldn't be unfamiliar with them, right?

454
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:38,110
Looks like I can't hide it anymore.

455
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:39,080
What?

456
00:22:48,710 --> 00:22:49,460
Indeed,

457
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:52,080
it was me and Mirror Commander.

458
00:22:52,610 --> 00:22:53,760
You're the Sword Master!

459
00:22:53,790 --> 00:22:54,960
How could you do such a thing?

460
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:55,660
Exactly.

461
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,430
Just because I'm the Sword Master,

462
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:59,330
why can't I be the Chief of Sects?

463
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:00,320
You...

464
00:23:00,650 --> 00:23:01,520
What?

465
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:04,440
Isn't the Chief of Sects

466
00:23:05,010 --> 00:23:06,230
supposed to be someone

467
00:23:06,230 --> 00:23:08,150
with real strength?

468
00:23:08,860 --> 00:23:10,500
Look at how chaotic the martial arts world became

469
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:12,420
during Feng Lie's leadership.

470
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:15,260
Since you all know now...

471
00:23:17,290 --> 00:23:18,240
Whatever.

472
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,680
I don't have time

473
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,000
to waste here with you.

474
00:23:24,990 --> 00:23:25,650
Trying to run away?

475
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:26,890
Wait.

476
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:34,700
Why didn't you fight back?

477
00:23:43,350 --> 00:23:44,550
Why do you have no martial arts skills at all?

478
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:46,060
He's no longer a threat.

479
00:23:46,390 --> 00:23:47,000
Let him go.

480
00:23:47,910 --> 00:23:48,910
Ye Yunqing.

481
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,260
What kind of trick are you playing?

482
00:23:56,190 --> 00:23:57,710
Because dealing with you folks

483
00:23:58,750 --> 00:24:00,490
doesn't require me to lift a finger.

484
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:11,580
Ye Yunqing,

485
00:24:12,710 --> 00:24:15,330
you should bear the consequences
of what you did back then.

486
00:24:16,390 --> 00:24:19,590
Today, don't blame me for being ruthless.
